Key steps in the project:
• Data Preparation: Loaded CSV, checked for missing values and duplicates
(none found).
• Data Cleaning: Renamed columns for clarity.
• Descriptive Statistics: Used describe() to understand averages and
distributions.
• Visualization:
o Bar plots for most & least populous countries.
o Sunburst and line charts for continent-level trends.
o Time series plots for global population growth.
Growth Analysis: Sorted countries by growth rate to find outliers.
Tools: Python, Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, Seaborn, Plotly.
